"2021-04-07T18:39:30.000Z","msg":"有冇人成世都無乜時期係開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630132ab25c66bdcca620cfc1fa68b946c3f4405","tid":2479332,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:40:33.000Z","msg":"中學唔開心之後先肯努力做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754add0b2d2c17fb163206b73b77a285b9794423","tid":2479332,"uid":367224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:43:16.000Z","msg":"高中就係<br />\n初中個人仲on99咁 老師都管得嚴啲<br />\n高中同學同老師都算係吹到兩句嘅朋友 又會一齊玩board game 自由好多"},{"pid":"25d73184225a9a6b5d987e60d6c3a9a5a1abe1ad","tid":2479332,"uid":367224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23cf67405edb1e50e572d5a9f7a3ebacb63e067a","tid":2479332,"uid":382353,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4d7802c328877cb79a0a5bdaa36f110614b0bef","tid":2479332,"uid":109050,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:09:04.000Z","msg":"正常 中學完左之後自己都變左<br />\n做人拘謹左好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:26:39.000Z","msg":"係 唔夠膽再講笑 粗口都越講越少<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:47:25.000Z","msg":"理論上中學畢業個人應該自由咗<br />\n但反而拘謹咗 越嚟越在意其他人目光 個人冇咁放鬆之餘仲唔知點解成日有啲不安 <br />\n本來以為考完dse之後啲不安會消失<br />\n加上人大多嘢煩 而家好難去appreciate life<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f04760919c7a3e2ca74de30262b69a1afb047f","tid":2479332,"uid":370123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:49:33.000Z","msg":"得確係，但你話搵到真心朋友係離開中學校園之後，雖然個真心朋友都係中學同學（中學時期唔係咁熟）"},{"pid":"ea9d907a3713c619df5d170075d5e4f205c84aa0","tid":2479332,"uid":94266,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T19:18:29.000Z","msg":"中學最後嗰年最開心，嗰年啲時間特別快過。<br />\n成績又好，連同學都羨慕我。<br />\n日日返學其中一個主要目的就係𥄫女。<br />\n又會有女自己走埋黎同我傾計。<br />\n溝唔溝到女冇所謂，反正我以後大把機會，遲啲再算。<br />\n又會幻想吓自己第日做乜做乜，充滿可以實現到既希望與期待。<br />\n成個feel好似自己係動畫裡面啲男主角咁，仲要差唔多日日都晴天。<br />\n<br />\n大咗：<br />\n冇晒希望，冇晒期待，好攰，好想9過，求其搵錢，過世算。"},{"pid":"aa7c650a0b286bdc618d0a25704ab70d4545f652","tid":2479332,"uid":301838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T19:30:13.000Z","msg":"有數學堂已經冇曬幻想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96794dc25258bbc81ff34e4646bf3fcfb33b7d8","tid":2479332,"uid":351117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T19:31:21.000Z","msg":"最憎 中學影響成世"},{"pid":"1b59d71dfb00d19d5dc8c998d71cdab13879315f","tid":2479332,"uid":351978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"050f4c1d862863cf3b836bbeb51043c39e687439","tid":2479332,"uid":366932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:18:16.000Z","msg":"中學得幾個fd <br />\n而家去哂英國讀<br />\n得返我on99喺香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T21:17:42.000Z","msg":"我都係，中學有好幾個friend喺中六開始都去咗外國讀書，淨返一兩個好friend嘅中同喺香港。加上無friend嘅 中同同我升同一間U，宜家比中學真係孤獨好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}